==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:8-->
The '''TechDraw Image''' tool inserts a [[Bitmap|bitmap]] image (PNG, TIFF, JPEG, etc.) from a file into the page as a view.

<!--T:25-->
{{Version|1.0}}: The [[TechDraw_View|TechDraw View]] tool can also create an Image View.

</translate>
